#Import data
setwd("~/Desktop/DS2")
DS2010_Warriors_Data <- read.csv("DS2010_Warriors_Data.csv")
dataG <- DS2010_Warriors_Data

Data Engineering

#Taking out redundant columns
dataG <- dataG[, -c(1, 3, 5, 25:41)]
# Making win(1) or loss(0) ---- 1 or 0
dataG$WL <- ifelse(dataG$WL == "W", 1, 0)
# Making X column "HomeAway" into 1 or 0 ---- home(1) / away(0)
colnames(dataG)[2] <- "HomeAway"

dataG$HomeAway <- ifelse(dataG$HomeAway == "@", 0, 1)

# The tree library
library(tree)

attach(dataG)

myTree = tree(GSWP~FG+FGP+X3P+X3Pper,dataG,minsize=50, mindev=.0001)

plot(dataG$FG,dataG$X3P)

partition.tree(myTree,add=TRUE,col='red')

plot(myTree)
text(myTree,pretty=1)

# Build the regression tree on the training set
library(rpart)
library(rpart.plot)
